Title: Take a Look Around
Description:
The Gala of Gifts is here to showcase the many wonderful artisans carefully crafting gifts just for you and your loved ones.

You should see what they have to offer, and talk to the other attendees. Who knows, you might just find the perfect gift for someone you care about!
ObjectivesText: Meet the vendors and visitors at the Gala of Gifts.
CompletionText: Have you seen all of the wares available?
RewardText:
Aren't the wares just marvelous? I find myself just a little jealous of the talent--and I find it hard to resist picking up everything they've made!

Did anything catch your eye?
